== 故事 ==
講述圍繞在擁有高知名度的律師，同時兼任米爾頓大學法律系教授的安娜莉絲·基汀，及其五位學生衛斯·吉賓斯、康納·沃許、米凱拉·普萊特、亞瑟·麥爾史東與蘿瑞爾·卡斯提洛和助手法蘭克·迪爾菲諾與邦妮·溫特巴頓之間的法律戰與凶殺案。第三季主軸圍繞在安娜莉絲家的致命火災，其中究竟有誰倖存，而誰又將因此失去性命，其中的真相又是什麼？

== 製作 ==
2016年3月3日，本劇獲得ABC第3季續訂。<ref name="Renewals S3"/><ref name="renewed" />

於[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]的訪問中，主理人[[彼得·諾沃克|彼得·諾沃克]]談論到第3季的走向。關於法蘭克的消失，他表示：「我可以看見3件西裝與護髮產品全散落一地，那更像法蘭克對自己的感覺」。至於安娜莉絲與法蘭克之間的信任問題，諾沃克說道：「法蘭克有兩個選擇：逃跑並期許安娜莉絲不會抓到他，或者他可以試圖贏回局面，但那會是段漫長的路。」<ref name="EW recap" />[[查理·韋伯|查理·韋伯]]談論到法蘭克的下落，他說：「我認為他躲起來了，而且是獨自一人。如果說他一條救命繩，我不認為那會是蘿瑞爾。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/03/17/how-get-away-murder-charlie-weber-frank-spoilers|title=How to Get Away with Murder star Charlie Weber on heartbreaking Frank twist|work=[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]|last=Abrams|first=Natalie|date=2016-03-17|accessdate=2016-03-18|archive-date=2016-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319044952/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/03/17/how-get-away-murder-charlie-weber-frank-spoilers|dead-url=no}}</ref>

關於蘿瑞爾，諾沃克表示本季將會探討她家族的背景故事並說道：「我覺得那非常重要，我們的節目承諾不會懸著伏筆太久，那是有可能探討的。我們已經提出這個問題很多次，遲早會給予答案。」而米凱拉的背景故事也將會有更多探討，諾沃克說：「我們有太多可以說，雅佳非常有天分，我很期待在明年可以深入探究她的個人生活。」<ref name="EW recap">{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/03/17/how-get-away-murder-finale-death-season-3-spoilers|title=How to Get Away with Murder postmortem: Who killed the latest victim?|work=娛樂周刊|last=Abrams|first=Natalie|date=2016-03-17|accessdate=2016-03-18|archive-date=2016-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319044808/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/03/17/how-get-away-murder-finale-death-season-3-spoilers|dead-url=no}}</ref>於[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]]的訪問中，諾沃克說將會揭露更多安娜莉絲與奈特的感情關係與他們的家庭。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/how-get-away-murder-creator-876452|title='How to Get Away With Murder' Creator Explains Killer Finale Twists|work=[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]]|last=Dowling|first=Amber|date=2016-03-17|accessdate=2016-03-18|archive-date=2016-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320224939/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/how-get-away-murder-creator-876452|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 選角 ===
第二季季終後，證實主要演員都將全數回歸本季。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/03/17/how-get-away-murder-finale-death-season-3-spoilers|title=How to Get Away with Murder postmortem: Who killed the latest victim?|work=娛樂周刊|last=Abrams|first=Natalie|date=2016-03-17|accessdate=2016-03-18|archive-date=2016-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319044808/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/03/17/how-get-away-murder-finale-death-season-3-spoilers|dead-url=no}}</ref>2016年3月18日，〈{{link-en|TVLine|TVLine}}〉公布[[柯納德·里嘉摩拉|康拉德·里卡摩拉]]將在本季被提升為常規演員。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2016/03/18/how-to-get-away-with-murder-season-3-conrad-ricamora-series-regular-oliver/|title=HTGAWM Promotes Conrad Ricamora to Series Regular in Season 3|work={{link-en|TVLine|TVLine}}|last=Ausiello|first=Michael|date=2016-03-18|accessdate=2016-03-18|archive-date=2016-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319211828/http://tvline.com/2016/03/18/how-to-get-away-with-murder-season-3-conrad-ricamora-series-regular-oliver/|dead-url=no}}</ref>7月20日，宣布《[[嗜血法醫|嗜血法醫]]》的{{link-en|勞倫·維萊斯|Lauren Vélez}}將飾演自信、友善、熱情與強大社交能力的米爾頓大學主席。<ref name="principal">{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2016/07/20/how-to-get-away-with-murder-season-3-cast-lauren-velez-htgawm/|title=HTGAWM Taps Dexter Alum To Recur as 'President' in Season 3|work=TVLine|last=Ausiello|first=Michael|date=2016-07-20|accessdate=2016-07-20|archive-date=2016-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160721112347/http://tvline.com/2016/07/20/how-to-get-away-with-murder-season-3-cast-lauren-velez-htgawm/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2016年8月6日，報導{{link-en|埃賽·莫拉萊斯|Esai Morales}}與{{link-en|艾美·麥蒂根|Amy Madigan}}將客串本季。<ref name="esai">{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2016/08/05/how-to-get-away-with-murder-season-3-esai-morales-cast/|title=HTGAWM Books NYPD Blue, Grey's Alums for Season 3 Guest Stints|work=TVLine|last=Ausiello|first=Michael|date=2016-08-05|accessdate=2016-08-06|archive-date=2016-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806152707/http://tvline.com/2016/08/05/how-to-get-away-with-murder-season-3-esai-morales-cast/|dead-url=no}}</ref>8月31日，宣布[[瑪麗·布萊姬|瑪麗·布萊姬]]將會客串第三季。<ref name="blige">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/08/mary-j-blige-guest-star-how-to-get-away-with-murder-viola-davis-shondaland-abc-1201810862/|title=Mary J. Blige To Guest Star In ‘How To Get Away With Murder’|work=Deadline|last=Petski|first=Denise|date=2016-08-31|accessdate=2016-08-31|archive-date=2016-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160901101755/http://deadline.com/2016/08/mary-j-blige-guest-star-how-to-get-away-with-murder-viola-davis-shondaland-abc-1201810862/|dead-url=no}}</ref>9月13日，宣布{{link-en|布莉特·巴特勒|Brett Butler}}將加入第三季飾演神秘角色。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2016/09/13/how-to-get-away-with-murder-brett-butler-cast-season-3/|title=''How to Get Away With Murder'' Casts Brett Butler in Season 3 Mystery Role|work=TV Line|last=Roots|first=Kimberly|date=2016-09-13|accessdate=2016-09-15|archive-date=2016-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160914121352/http://tvline.com/2016/09/13/how-to-get-away-with-murder-brett-butler-cast-season-3/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

